# Documentation maintenance

When you change matched files, read [docs/AGENTS_MAINTENANCE.md](docs/AGENTS_MAINTENANCE.md) and update docs in the **same PR**.

## Always check

- [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) — CLI/API, env vars, repo map, implemented vs planned
- Bump **Last verified** in AGENTS.md; run `poetry run python scripts/verify_agents_md.py`

## Also update when relevant

| Change | Doc |
|--------|-----|
| Agent tools, prompts, memory | [docs/AGENT_PLAN.md](docs/AGENT_PLAN.md) |
| Feature shipped or phase completed | [docs/PLAN.md](docs/PLAN.md) |
| Planned feature partial/full delivery | [docs/NEW_FEATURES_PLAN.md](docs/NEW_FEATURES_PLAN.md) |
| User-facing commands or deploy steps | [README.md](README.md), [SETUP.md](SETUP.md) |
| This repo's goals/priorities | [DIRECTION.md](DIRECTION.md) |

Do not duplicate PLAN.md into AGENTS.md — index and link.
